The Glenn Beck Program



The Glenn Beck Radio Program, Monday through Friday, 9am - 12pm ET




        
      
The Glenn Beck Program - 1/24/14Friday


Glenn and the guys talk about the recent news of Justin Beiber's arrest
      and if his actions are spiraling towards a bad ending.

  Also, Mayor Deblasio of New York has come out in support of
      NY Governor Andrew Cuomo's extremist remarks against conservatives, 
        and this just solidifies where the state of NY is going.

  Plus, the madness of how government spends money,
     and a sperm donor's story of how he's being forced to pay child support.
